org.eclipse.stardust.engine.api.runtime

Interface ProcessInstanceLinkType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface ProcessInstanceLinkType
extends Serializable
    Specifies the type of link that associates one process instance to another. There are several predefined link types:
    • switch - a process instance was aborted and execution switched to another process instance.
    • join - a process instance has joined as subprocess another process instance.
    • upgrade - a process instance has been upgraded to a new process definition.
    • spawn - a process instance has been started as peer of another process instance.
